short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that replaces Communities on Roblox back to Groups!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Very simple extension that can replace "Communities" on the Roblox website with "Groups" or an another name.

Source code of this project is available on GitHub: https://github.com/EfazDev/efazdev-cdn/tree/main/cdn/extensions/communities-renamer/chromeExtension
